section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/alchemist-derth.lua"

t("Pfaugh. You're too late. %s has already finished. But I suppose it doesn't do any harm to take these and give you your undeserved reward.", "Pfaugh. You're too late. %s has already finished. But I suppose it doesn't do any harm to take these and give you your undeserved reward.")
t("Ah, excellent. Hand them over, if you please. You should know that in your overlong absence, %s has managed to create a %s. I'll be most put out if he steals my rightful spot.", "Ah, excellent. Hand them over, if you please. You should know that in your overlong absence, %s has managed to create a %s. I'll be most put out if he steals my rightful spot.")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A human robed in immaculate white satin opens the door and eyes you appraisingly.*#WHITE#
Ah, an adventurer. I was just thinking that I needed a new one.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A human robed in immaculate white satin opens the door and eyes you appraisingly.*#WHITE#
Ah, an adventurer. I was just thinking that I needed a new one.]])
t("That sounds promising. And ominous.", "That sounds promising. And ominous.")
t("Indeed, it is both promising and ominous. I can reward you handsomely for your efforts, but they will lead you into deadly peril to which, I assume, the previous three fellows who went off on my errand never to return can attest.", "Indeed, it is both promising and ominous. I can reward you handsomely for your efforts, but they will lead you into deadly peril to which, I assume, the previous three fellows who went off on my errand never to return can attest.")
t("What do you propose?", "What do you propose?")
t("Good adventurer, I am an alchemist, and quite a good one. This year, for the first time, the great Brotherhood of Alchemists has invited my application to their number. I'll not try your patience with the details of the application process, but suffice to say that it is grueling. Fortunately, a mere three tasks now stand between me and acceptance.", "Good adventurer, I am an alchemist, and quite a good one. This year, for the first time, the great Brotherhood of Alchemists has invited my application to their number. I'll not try your patience with the details of the application process, but suffice to say that it is grueling. Fortunately, a mere three tasks now stand between me and acceptance.")
t("How can I help?", "How can I help?")
t("I require ingredients for three potent mixtures. Obviously, since I seek your aid, none of them is to be found by simply strolling to the local herbalist's. No, they will need to be forcibly parted from their owners who will, just as obviously, put up a fight. I've yet to encounter a naga who would be persuaded to hand over his tongue! Ha! Oh, I am droll at times.", "I require ingredients for three potent mixtures. Obviously, since I seek your aid, none of them is to be found by simply strolling to the local herbalist's. No, they will need to be forcibly parted from their owners who will, just as obviously, put up a fight. I've yet to encounter a naga who would be persuaded to hand over his tongue! Ha! Oh, I am droll at times.")
t("I specialize in separating vital body parts from monsters. What do you offer in return?", "I specialize in separating vital body parts from monsters. What do you offer in return?")
t("Why, I will let you share in the fruits of my labors! Each of the three mixtures I shall produce in a quantity sufficient to create three doses: one for me, one for the Brotherhood and their confounded trial... and one for you. I must tell you that time is of the essence. I am not the only one who the Brotherhood invited this year, yet they will accept only one applicant-- the first to complete their trials. I know of at least three others laboring furiously to take my rightful place. Should your aid see me through, then I will reward you beyond even the remarkable elixirs. I've an ancient Lifebinding Emerald that grants great powers of health and healing when used properly. What say you?", "Why, I will let you share in the fruits of my labors! Each of the three mixtures I shall produce in a quantity sufficient to create three doses: one for me, one for the Brotherhood and their confounded trial... and one for you. I must tell you that time is of the essence. I am not the only one who the Brotherhood invited this year, yet they will accept only one applicant-- the first to complete their trials. I know of at least three others laboring furiously to take my rightful place. Should your aid see me through, then I will reward you beyond even the remarkable elixirs. I've an ancient Lifebinding Emerald that grants great powers of health and healing when used properly. What say you?")
t("I accept.", "I accept.")
t("I cannot aid you at this time.", "I cannot aid you at this time.")
t("Excellent. Now then, I've three elixirs I'm working on. I'll burden you with only one at a time, since I've learned the hard way about the hazards of overloading an adventurer's brain. Here are your options: the elixir of the fox, which makes you as nimble and cunning as a fox; the elixir of avoidance, which sharpens your natural inclinations to get out of the way of incoming harm; or the elixir of precision, which grants intuitive understanding of an enemy's most sensitive spots. Which would you like to aid me with?", "Excellent. Now then, I've three elixirs I'm working on. I'll burden you with only one at a time, since I've learned the hard way about the hazards of overloading an adventurer's brain. Here are your options: the elixir of the fox, which makes you as nimble and cunning as a fox; the elixir of avoidance, which sharpens your natural inclinations to get out of the way of incoming harm; or the elixir of precision, which grants intuitive understanding of an enemy's most sensitive spots. Which would you like to aid me with?")
t("Here's a list of the ingredients I'm missing. Please attempt to not lose your life in their pursuit. I'll be most put out if I must wait another year. Oh, and I suppose I should tell you that I've already a handful of adventurers out scouring the unpleasant places of the world for these ingredients. Dally and one of them shall claim the prize while you're out.", "Here's a list of the ingredients I'm missing. Please attempt to not lose your life in their pursuit. I'll be most put out if I must wait another year. Oh, and I suppose I should tell you that I've already a handful of adventurers out scouring the unpleasant places of the world for these ingredients. Dally and one of them shall claim the prize while you're out.")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*The door is locked and nobody responds to your knocks*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*The door is locked and nobody responds to your knocks*#WHITE#")
t("[Leave]", "[Leave]")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist opens his door.*#WHITE#
Ah, you again.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist opens his door.*#WHITE#
Ah, you again.]])
t("I've returned with the ingredients for the %s.", "I've returned with the ingredients for the %s.")
t("I've come to offer more aid.", "I've come to offer more aid.")
t("[Give him the monster bits.]", "[Give him the monster bits.]")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist grins and motions impatiently for the ingredients.*#WHITE#
Wonderful, absolutely wonderful! The final step! Here, let me have those!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist grins and motions impatiently for the ingredients.*#WHITE#
Wonderful, absolutely wonderful! The final step! Here, let me have those!]])
t("[Give him the monster bits]", "[Give him the monster bits]")
t("Wait here while I perform my art. I'll have your reward within the hour.", "Wait here while I perform my art. I'll have your reward within the hour.")
t("A final wait for you, my good adventurer, and then I shall return with both your rewards! Haha, complete at last!", "A final wait for you, my good adventurer, and then I shall return with both your rewards! Haha, complete at last!")
t("[Wait]", "[Wait]")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns and hands you a small vial of fine glass.*#WHITE#
Enjoy your reward.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns and hands you a small vial of fine glass.*#WHITE#
Enjoy your reward.]])
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns with a vial and a green gem.*#WHITE#
Enjoy the fruits of your labors, adventurer. I know I will. To show my appreciation, I shall name my firstborn after... er, what was your name, then? Haha, I jest. Oh, I do go on when I'm giddy. Fare you well.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns with a vial and a green gem.*#WHITE#
Enjoy the fruits of your labors, adventurer. I know I will. To show my appreciation, I shall name my firstborn after... er, what was your name, then? Haha, I jest. Oh, I do go on when I'm giddy. Fare you well.]])
t("Thank you. I'll be off.", "Thank you. I'll be off.")
t("Excellent. With which would you like to aid me?", "Excellent. With which would you like to aid me?")
