t("Oh, easy. You get a swig of each brew, of course. They'll put hair on your chest, and possibly your eyelids and fingernails. And, if your aid proves the deciding factor, then I've got a real treat for you: perhaps the last Taint of Purging left in Maj'Eyal.", "Oh, easy. You get a swig of each brew, of course. They'll put hair on your chest, and possibly your eyelids and fingernails. And, if your aid proves the deciding factor, then I've got a real treat for you: perhaps the last Taint of Purging left in Maj'Eyal.")
