t("Curse the earth around you in a radius of %d for %d turns. Any who stand upon it are weakened, reducing the damage they inflict by %d%%", "Curse the earth around you in a radius of %d for %d turns. Any who stand upon it are weakened, reducing the damage they inflict by %d%%")
