t("The Master", "The Master")
t("A terrifying vampiric figure of power, with flowing robes and an intense aura of fright.  His cold, sinewy flesh seems to cling to this world through greed and malice, and his eyes betray a strength of mind beyond any puny mortal.  All nearby are utterly subservient to his will, though he stands aloof from them, as if to say he needs not the pathetic meddling of minions to help him overcome his foes.  Your eyes are drawn to a dark staff in his hands which seems to suck the very life from the air around it.  It looks ancient and dangerous and terrible, and the sight of it fills you with fervent desire.", "A terrifying vampiric figure of power, with flowing robes and an intense aura of fright.  His cold, sinewy flesh seems to cling to this world through greed and malice, and his eyes betray a strength of mind beyond any puny mortal.  All nearby are utterly subservient to his will, though he stands aloof from them, as if to say he needs not the pathetic meddling of minions to help him overcome his foes.  Your eyes are drawn to a dark staff in his hands which seems to suck the very life from the air around it.  It looks ancient and dangerous and terrible, and the sight of it fills you with fervent desire.")
